        S21["STAGE 1 вҖ” Per-Cue Evidence\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nCueEvidencePacket\ncues: list of {\n  cue_id: str\n  modality_family: str\n  x: float          вҶҗ raw cue value\n  d_i: float        вҶҗ effect size weight\n  reliability_w: float  вҶҗ cue reliability\n  llr_raw: float    вҶҗ log-likelihood ratio\n}\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\npublish: fusion.evidence.ready"]

        S21 -->|"baseline.ready = true\n(90-180s stats available)\npublish: fusion.normalized.ready"| S22

        S22["STAGE 2 вҖ” Baseline Normalization\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nNormalizedEvidencePacket\ncues: list of {\n  cue_id: str\n  modality_family: str\n  z_i: float        вҶҗ robust z-score\n  median: float     вҶҗ from baseline window\n  mad: float        вҶҗ median absolute deviation\n  d_i: float\n  reliability_w: float\n}\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nFORMULA:\nz_i = (x вҲ’ median_baseline) / (1.4826 Г— MAD + Оө)\n\nBaseline window: rolling 90вҖ“180s\nNormalization: Robust Z (NOT standard Z)\nOutlier resistance via MAD not std"]

        S22 -->|"each window update\npublish: fusion.posterior.updated"| S23

        S23["STAGE 3 вҖ” Bayesian Log-Odds Accumulation\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nPosteriorPacket\nlog_odds: float\nposterior: float\ncontributing_cues: list[{cue_id, contribution}]\nactive_families: set[str]\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nFORMULA (per window):\nlogit(P) = logit(0.30) + ОЈ [ w_i Г— (d_i Г— z_i вҲ’ d_iВІ/2) ]\nposterior = sigmoid(log_odds)\n\nPrior: 0.30 (not 0.50 вҖ” avoids overconfidence)\nw_i  = reliability_w per cue\nd_i  = effect size weight\nz_i  = baseline-normalized cue value\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nRolling: accumulates per question window\nTop contributors ranked by |w_i Г— d_i Г— z_i|"]

        S23 -->|"check gate conditions\nevery update cycle"| S24

        S24{"STAGE 4 вҖ” Convergence Gate\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nDecisionPacket\nposterior: float\npassed: bool\nfamilies_count: int\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nGATE RULE:\npassed = (posterior > 0.65)\n       AND (active_families вүҘ 2)\n\nRequires 2+ independent modality\nfamilies to prevent single-channel\nfalse alarms"}

        S24 -->|"passed = false\ncontinue accumulating"| LOOP["accumulate next window\nвҶ’ back to Stage 3"]
        LOOP --> S23
    end

    S24 -->|"passed = true\npublish: decision.ready"| S25

